He did the former. It cost Thirty five pounds, but he said he would have nothing except the Medalls. He went next Summer to England, was treated as usual & she being then Queen, the Dean was promis'd a Settlement in England, but return'd as he went, & instead of Favour or Medalls hath been ever since under her Majesties Displeasure.····· ···· the Medalls were ·······
